my performance versus Jonah...

274
00:09:57.097 --> 00:09:59.997
- Uh. okay.

275
00:09:59.999 --> 00:10:01.599
- Yeah. you better hurry up.
girl.

276
00:10:01.600 --> 00:10:03.167
You better get that TV.

277
00:10:03.168 --> 00:10:05.698
