Please. I'm begging you!

278
00:10:05.703 --> 00:10:07.837
- She's very... she's...
They're very pretty. yep.

279
00:10:07.838 --> 00:10:09.738
- Ow! Frank!

280
00:10:09.739 --> 00:10:10.869
- Y'all don't want to do this.

281
00:10:10.873 --> 00:10:12.107
Please!

282
00:10:13.108 --> 00:10:15.576
