00:10:28.954 --> 00:10:30.721
- It might be. yes.

290
00:10:30.722 --> 00:10:33.222
All right. Punctuality.

291
00:10:33.224 --> 00:10:35.058
I do not tolerate it.

292
00:10:35.059 --> 00:10:37.589
